item.title: CVE-2020-6215|2024-08-04T08:55:22.077Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20netweaver%20as%20abap%20%28business%20server%20pages%20test%20application%20it00%29
item.description: SAP NetWeaver AS ABAP Business Server Pages Test Application IT00, versions 700, 701, 702, 730, 731, 740, 750, 751, 752, 753, 754, allows an attacker to redirect users to a malicious site due to insufficient URL validation and steal credentials of the victim, leading to URL Redirection vulnerability.
